{"name":"iSnap Social","permalink":"isnap","crunchbase_url":"http://www.crunchbase.com/company/isnap","homepage_url":"http://www.isnapsocial.com","blog_url":"http://www.isnapsocial.com/index.php/blog/","blog_feed_url":"","twitter_username":"isnapsocial","category_code":"public_relations","number_of_employees":null,"founded_year":2010,"founded_month":null,"founded_day":null,"deadpooled_year":null,"deadpooled_month":null,"deadpooled_day":null,"deadpooled_url":null,"tag_list":"social-media, social-media-marketing, kiosks","alias_list":null,"email_address":"corp@isnapsocial.com","phone_number":"916-333-0330","description":"Social media marketing tools","created_at":"Sat Jul 14 03:29:48 UTC 2012","updated_at":"Thu Nov 08 02:07:17 UTC 2012","overview":"<p>iSnap Social is the creator of the social photo station and accompanying suite of social media marketing tools. iSnap Social products enable brands to create more authentic connections with customers through photo sharing. </p>\n\n<p>For consumers, iSnap is a popular social sharing experience that is fun and simple. For marketers, iSnap activates brand advocates, distributes promos and offers, captures analytics and demographics and generates new Likes, Followers, and Checkins.</p>\n\n<p>The iSnap Social Photo Station is the unique touch point that engages users and entices them to become brand ambassadors by becoming social media fans and followers. By generating great photo content and sharing it with their individual networks, iSnap users are creating the social media buzz around the brand, instead of a marketer. This results in a more authentic connection between the brand and its target market.</p>\n\n<p>Posting a picture with the Social Photo Station is as easy as 1, 2, 3. One, snap a picture. Two, select a social network to share on. Three, write a short message and hit post! The user gets an enjoyable way to take high quality photos, branded with your graphic overlays, and share them with friends instantly. Brands get a unique way to engage with customers, additional fans and followers automatically, and insightful data into who their guests are.</p>","image":{"available_sizes":[[[150,50],"assets/images/resized/0020/1333/201333v2-max-150x150.png"],[[180,61],"assets/images/resized/0020/1333/201333v2-max-250x250.png"],[[180,61],"assets/images/resized/0020/1333/201333v2-max-450x450.png"]],"attribution":null},"products":[],"relationships":[{"is_past":false,"title":"CEO","person":{"first_name":"Alexander","last_name":"Lowe","permalink":"alexander-lowe","image":null}},{"is_past":false,"title":"Director of Channel","person":{"first_name":"Mike","last_name":"Delautre","permalink":"mike-delautre","image":null}},{"is_past":false,"title":"Communications Manager/Media Contact","person":{"first_name":"Julia","last_name":"Mjehovich","permalink":"julia-mjehovich","image":{"available_sizes":[[[129,150],"assets/images/resized/0021/9070/219070v2-max-150x150.jpg"],[[213,246],"assets/images/resized/0021/9070/219070v2-max-250x250.jpg"],[[213,246],"assets/images/resized/0021/9070/219070v2-max-450x450.jpg"]],"attribution":""}}},{"is_past":false,"title":"Director of Product","person":{"first_name":"Dat","last_name":"Tau","permalink":"dat-tau","image":null}},{"is_past":false,"title":"System Engineer","person":{"first_name":"Andrew","last_name":"Moon","permalink":"andrew-moon-2","image":null}}],"competitions":[],"providerships":[],"total_money_raised":"$0","funding_rounds":[],"investments":[],"acquisition":null,"acquisitions":[],"offices":[{"description":"","address1":"","address2":"","zip_code":"","city":"Sacramento","state_code":"CA","country_code":"USA","latitude":null,"longitude":null}],"milestones":[],"ipo":null,"video_embeds":[],"screenshots":[{"available_sizes":[[[112,150],"assets/images/resized/0020/0914/200914v2-max-150x150.jpg"],[[186,250],"assets/images/resized/0020/0914/200914v2-max-250x250.jpg"],[[336,450],"assets/images/resized/0020/0914/200914v2-max-450x450.jpg"]],"attribution":null},